* A new [[Part_EditAttachment#Attachment_modes|attachment mode]] called ''XY parallel to plane'' was added to the Engine Plane and Engine 3D. It results in an attachment similar to ''Object's XY'' but with the XY plane translated to pass through a selected vertex. In contrast to the ''Translate origin'' attachment mode, it does not move the origin in 2D/Sketcher. It can be used with origin planes, datum planes and sketches, but also with any object with a ''Placement'' property. [https://github.com/FreeCAD/FreeCAD/pull/14372 Pull request #14372]
